        <div class="col-lg-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12" id="c1" style="text-align: center;">
          <br>
          <p style="font-family: PlayfairDisplay-Regular; line-height: 1.5;">
            I got thrown into unemployment from one day to another. First, it was hard to accept the emptiness and abundance of time. After a few days of doing nothing, I contacted every single person that I have ever talked to on    facebook – and all of them replied. 
            <br>
            <br>
            Most of them were in the same situation and we felt an exciting connection. It was amazing to see how conversations went from simply saying “How are you going” to a lot more meaningful chats. I really cared for their stories and I had the time to listen to them. 
            <br>
            <br>
            It gave me great comfort to know that there are people who share the same feelings. From now on, I will always take enough time to talk to my friends.
            <br>
            <br>
            Tamara
          </p>
